  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager (Workplace Office)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>We are seeking a proactive and results-driven Business Development Manage<strong>r</strong> to join our team in the interior design industry (commerical office fit out). This role involves identifying new business opportunities, nurturing client relationships, and supporting the Director in strategic growth initiatives.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proactively identify and pursue new business leads through various marketing strategies and networking opportunities.</p></li><li><p>Secure meetings with clients or consultants, deliver compelling presentations, and introduce the company’s products and services.</p></li><li><p>Prepare business proposals, presentations, quotations, and budgets independently.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with technical and design departments to deliver tailored proposals that meet client requirements.</p></li><li><p>Represent the company at meetings, exhibitions, conferences, and other events.</p></li><li><p>Manage the full tender process: sourcing, costing, pricing strategies, and timely submissions.</p></li><li><p>Ensure accurate and timely preparation of quotations or tenders in line with client/consultant timelines.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Bachelor's Degree in Business Studies, Marketing, or a related field.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 5 years of experience in Business Development or Sales, preferably within the Interior Design, Construction, or Property industry.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and presentation skills with a client-focused mindset.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and collaboratively in a fast-paced environment.</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates please apply online or send your latest CV to <strong>alex.fong@AlwaysHired.com.sg</strong></p><p>AlwaysHired Pte Ltd</p><p>Reg No: R1549345</p><p>EA: 24C2293</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Please note that your response to this advertisement will constitute informed consent to the collection, use, and/or disclosure of personal data by AlwaysHired, its affiliates and, where necessary, to relevant third parties, for purposes such as job application processing, career advisory, research, and other administrative purposes, in compliance with the relevant provisions of the Privacy Policy available at www.alwayshired.com.sg/privacy-policy</em></p>",
